Clinical Effect of Lamivudine Combined with Leflunomide and Methylprednisolone 
Tablets in the Treatment of Hepatitis B Virus-Associated Glomerulonephritis and 
Its Influence on Renal Function Indicators.

Liu H(1), Jiang F(2), Zheng K(3), Zhang M(4), Xing X(5), Zhou C(6).

Author information:
(1)Department of Clinical Laboratory, Yantai Affiliated Hospital of Binzhou 
Medical University, 264100 Yantai, Shandong, China.
(2)Hepatology Department (I), Yantai Qishan Hospital, 264000 Yantai, Shandong, 
China.
(3)PICC Clinic, Affiliated Qingdao Central Hospital of Qingdao University, 
Qingdao Cancer Hospital, 266000 Qingdao, Shandong, China.
(4)Department of Health Management, Jinan Zhangqiu District People's Hospital, 
