Hospital medical care and the COVID-19 mortality in METEOR partner countries 
(the Netherlands, Belgium, Italy, And Poland).

Kowalska M(1), de Winter P(2)(3)(4), Godderis L(5)(6), Boone A(5), Szemik S(1).

Author information:
(1)The Medical University of Silesia in Katowice, Katowice, Poland (Department 
