Recommendations for the Screening of Breast Cancer of the Brazilian College of 
Radiology and Diagnostic Imaging, Brazilian Society of Mastology and Brazilian 
Federation of Gynecology and Obstetrics Association.

Urban LABD(1), Chala LF(2), Paula IB(1), Bauab SDP(1), Schaefer MB(1), Oliveira 
ALK(1), Shimizu C(1), Oliveira TMG(1), Moraes PC(1), Miranda BMM(1), Aduan 
FE(1), Rego SJF(1), Canella EO(1), Couto HL(3), Badan GM(3), Francisco JLE(4), 
